    "To complement the redshift-based formulation of the equation of state, we also derive an exact expression for the EUP-induced equation of state parameter in terms of the scale factor a.",
    "By expressing the modified Friedmann equations in terms of a = 1 1+z, and following the same thermodynamic procedure, we obtain",
