    "We consider natural cutoffs as a generic dynamical effect in the context of EUP model, therefore its equation of state parameter w ≡ p ρ will be a function of time.",
    "In this respect, p is the pressure and ρ is the energy density of the energy density of matter, modified by quantum gravitational effects, drives the observed accelerated expansion of the universe."
